*   **"Herb Sutter cppfront"**
    *   Herb Sutter’s `cppfront` (a C++ to C++ source-to-source compiler for safer C++) has been in development for years. It remains an experimental project. The mention of it as a "potentially new syntax" is consistent with the 2020s.

*   **"Carbon language"**
    *   Carbon is a successor to C++ being developed by Google. It has been in active development since 2021. The mention of it as a "new C++ compatible language" is current.

