### 4. Synthesis and Date Estimation

*   **Latest Possible Date:** **March 2024** (when TAIT was stabilized). The author calls TAIT "forthcoming."
*   **Earliest Possible Date:** **May 2023** (when GATs were stabilized). The author calls GATs "recently landed."
